  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1-5. Paṭhamaāghātapaṭivinayasuttādivaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "161-165"
      },
      ". Dutiyassa ",
      " paṭhame natthi vattabbaṃ. Dutiye āghāto paṭivinayati ettha, etehīti vā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "āghātapaṭivinayā"
      },
      ". Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘āghāto etehi paṭivinetabbo’’"
      },
      "tiādi."
    ],
    "innerText": "161-165. Dutiyassa paṭhame natthi vattabbaṃ. Dutiye āghāto paṭivinayati ettha, etehīti vā āghātapaṭivinayā. Tenāha ‘‘āghāto etehi paṭivinetabbo’’tiādi."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Nantaka"
      },
      "nti anantakaṃ, antavirahitaṃ vatthakhaṇḍaṃ. Yadi hi tassa anto bhaveyya, ‘‘pilotikā’’ti saṅkhaṃ na gaccheyya."
    ],
    "innerText": "Nantakanti anantakaṃ, antavirahitaṃ vatthakhaṇḍaṃ. Yadi hi tassa anto bhaveyya, ‘‘pilotikā’’ti saṅkhaṃ na gaccheyya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sevālenā"
      },
      "ti bījakaṇṇikakesarādibhedena sevālena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Udakapappaṭakenā"
      },
      "ti nīlamaṇḍūkapiṭṭhivaṇṇena udakapiṭṭhiṃ chādetvā nibbattena udakapiṭṭhikena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ghammena anugato"
      },
      "ti ghammena phuṭṭho abhibhūto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cittuppāda"
      },
      "nti paṭighasampayuttacittuppādaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Sevālenāti bījakaṇṇikakesarādibhedena sevālena. Udakapappaṭakenāti nīlamaṇḍūkapiṭṭhivaṇṇena udakapiṭṭhiṃ chādetvā nibbattena udakapiṭṭhikena. Ghammena anugatoti ghammena phuṭṭho abhibhūto. Cittuppādanti paṭighasampayuttacittuppādaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Visabhāgavedanuppattiyā kakaceneva iriyāpathapavattinivāraṇena chindanto ābādhati pīḷetīti ābādho, so assa atthīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ābādhiko"
      },
      ". Taṃsamuṭṭhānena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dukkhito"
      },
      " sañjātadukkho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bāḷhagilāno"
      },
      "ti adhimattagilāno. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Gāmantanāyakassā"
      },
      "ti gāmantasampāpakassa."
    ],
    "innerText": "Visabhāgavedanuppattiyā kakaceneva iriyāpathapavattinivāraṇena chindanto ābādhati pīḷetīti ābādho, so assa atthīti ābādhiko. Taṃsamuṭṭhānena dukkhito sañjātadukkho. Bāḷhagilānoti adhimattagilāno. Gāmantanāyakassāti gāmantasampāpakassa."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Pasannabhāvena ",
      " udakassa acchabhāvo veditabboti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘acchodakāti pasannodakā’’"
      },
      "ti. Sādurasatāya sātatāti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘madhurodakā’’"
      },
      "ti. Tanukameva salilaṃ visesato sītalaṃ, na bahalāti āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘tanusītasalilā’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Setakā"
      },
      "ti nikkaddamā. Sacikkhallādivasena hi udakassa vivaṇṇatā. Sabhāvato pana taṃ setavaṇṇameva. Tatiyādīni uttānatthāneva."
    ],
    "innerText": "Pasannabhāvena udakassa acchabhāvo veditabboti āha ‘‘acchodakāti pasannodakā’’ti. Sādurasatāya sātatāti āha ‘‘madhurodakā’’ti. Tanukameva salilaṃ visesato sītalaṃ, na bahalāti āha ‘‘tanusītasalilā’’ti. Setakāti nikkaddamā. Sacikkhallādivasena hi udakassa vivaṇṇatā. Sabhāvato pana taṃ setavaṇṇameva. Tatiyādīni uttānatthāneva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Paṭhamaāghātapaṭivinayasuttādivaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Nirodhasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "166"
      },
      ". Chaṭṭhe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "amarisanatthe"
      },
      "ti asahanatthe. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anāgatavacanaṃ kata"
      },
      "nti anāgatasaddappayogo kato, attho pana vattamānakālikova. Akkharacintakā (pāṇini. 3.3.145-146) hi īdisesu ṭhānesu anokappanāmarisanatthavasena atthisadde upapade vattamānakālepi anāgatavacanaṃ karonti."
    ],
    "innerText": "166. Chaṭṭhe amarisanattheti asahanatthe. Anāgatavacanaṃ katanti anāgatasaddappayogo kato, attho pana vattamānakālikova. Akkharacintakā (pāṇini. 3.3.145-146) hi īdisesu ṭhānesu anokappanāmarisanatthavasena atthisadde upapade vattamānakālepi anāgatavacanaṃ karonti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Nirodhasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "7-9. Codanāsuttādivaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "167-9"
      },
      ". Sattame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vatthusandassanā"
      },
      "ti yasmiṃ vatthusmiṃ āpatti, tassa sarūpato dassanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Āpattisandassanā"
      },
      "ti yaṃ āpattiṃ so āpanno, tassā dassanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṃvāsappaṭikkhepo"
      },
      "ti uposathappavāraṇādisaṃvāsassa paṭikkhipanaṃ akaraṇaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sāmīcippaṭikkhepo"
      },
      "ti abhivādanādisāmīcikiriyāya akaraṇaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Codayamānenā"
      },
      "ti codentena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cuditakassa kālo"
      },
      "ti cuditakassa codetabbakālo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Puggala"
      },
      "nti codetabbapuggalaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Upaparikkhitvā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘ayaṃ cuditakalakkhaṇe tiṭṭhati, na tiṭṭhatī’’ti vīmaṃsitvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ayasaṃ āropetī"
      },
      "ti ‘‘ime maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhantā ayasaṃ byasanaṃ uppādentī’’ti bhikkhūnaṃ ayasaṃ uppādeti. Aṭṭhamanavamāni uttānatthāneva."
    ],
    "innerText": "167-9. Sattame vatthusandassanāti yasmiṃ vatthusmiṃ āpatti, tassa sarūpato dassanaṃ. Āpattisandassanāti yaṃ āpattiṃ so āpanno, tassā dassanaṃ. Saṃvāsappaṭikkhepoti uposathappavāraṇādisaṃvāsassa paṭikkhipanaṃ akaraṇaṃ. Sāmīcippaṭikkhepoti abhivādanādisāmīcikiriyāya akaraṇaṃ. Codayamānenāti codentena. Cuditakassa kāloti cuditakassa codetabbakālo. Puggalanti codetabbapuggalaṃ. Upaparikkhitvāti ‘‘ayaṃ cuditakalakkhaṇe tiṭṭhati, na tiṭṭhatī’’ti vīmaṃsitvā. Ayasaṃ āropetīti ‘‘ime maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhantā ayasaṃ byasanaṃ uppādentī’’ti bhikkhūnaṃ ayasaṃ uppādeti. Aṭṭhamanavamāni uttānatthāneva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Codanāsuttādivaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
